author: RTÉ News
title: Measures lifted in Wuhan, costs of lockdown in focus
description: Residents of China's Wuhan city have mixed emotions as containment measures are lifted and the community infection rate slows to a trickle, some praising the government and others rueing the economic costs.
content:
